cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.SY 

The paper deals with techniques for automatically inferring invariant properties of feed-forward neural networks. This falls under the broad category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also applies the techniques on networks for the MNIST and ACASXU applications, which are related to computer vision (cs.CV) and cybersecurity (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of invariants for providing robustness guarantees and simplifying proofs, which are relevant to control systems (cs.SY).
